{"tid":1389374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美官員透露中国共軍集結香港邊界  白宮密切關注","createTime":"2019-07-31T01:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T07:42:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"54b4c31325814a37747887667e2dea236fbeb321","tid":1389374,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:38:44.000Z","msg":"香港反送中抗爭愈演愈烈，不斷爆發警民衝突，中國中央也開始發出警告言論，有美國官員向外媒透露，中國解放軍已集結香港邊界，白宮正在密切關注。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報導，美國官員表示，白宮正在監視於香港邊境集結的中國軍隊。這幾週香港警察與抗爭者發生暴力衝突，中國週一警告，香港動亂已非和平抗爭。報導指出，美國官員表示，中國軍隊或武警已集結在香港邊境，性質仍不明。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，中國政府將香港動亂推託為美國的責任，但美國官員否認。美國總統川普在香港事件上的發言相當謹慎，僅讚揚了中國領導人習近平的「克制」，目前尚不清楚若中國軍隊介入香港，白宮會如何對應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2869033\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2869033&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047IjxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=a51f501c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2869033&h=bba70efe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2869033</a>"},{"pid":"da025670c47769506f51130fc4b2422b72918c64","tid":1389374,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:49:05.000Z","msg":"蠢蠢欲動"},{"pid":"c44a2055fca996f1f983ddaf3a489271a4a9c072","tid":1389374,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:56:53.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"bcfd50d0c94958491805f0292840eac8567d34a6","tid":1389374,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:57:46.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"50da0975c4c01f0210d9a82ff5fd5b8e00112a5f","tid":1389374,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:58:01.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"7b054b2fd88622031d168adc4b4dd8ebcfd3a77a","tid":1389374,"uid":253954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:58:53.000Z"